News.Title: Urban Enviro Waste Management Secures 7.7 Crore Rupee Order
News.Summary: Urban Enviro Waste Management, a company with a market capitalization of 140 crore rupees, has won an order worth 7.7 crore rupees. The company operates in the Small and Medium Enterprise (SME) sector.

News.Title: Urban Enviro Waste Management Secures 50 Crore Rupee Order
News.Summary: Urban Enviro Waste Management, a company with a market capitalization of 270 crore rupees, has won a significant order worth 50 crore rupees. This development is particularly noteworthy for the company, which is listed in the Small and Medium Enterprise (SME) segment.
